projects.name: WeWork
projects.description: A WeWork é uma rede global de espaços de trabalho em que empresas e pessoas crescem juntas.

projects.name: Slack
projects.description: When your team needs to kick off a project, hire a new employee, deploy some code, review a sales contract, finalize next year's budget, measure an A/B test, plan your next office opening, and more, Slack has you covered.

projects.name: NIO
projects.description: A empresa chinesa que migrou para os Estados Unidos há dois anos desenvolve veículos autônomos, elétricos e inteligentes.

projects.name: Rubrick
projects.description: A startup ajuda empresas a organizar seus dados com aplicativos de recuperação, análise e desenvolvimento de arquivos em nuvem.

news.title: Notícia 1
news.content: The following is an alphabetical list of the minor characters in the various versions of The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy, by Douglas Adams. The descriptions of the characters are accompanied by information on details about appearances and references to the characters. Major characters— Arthur Dent, Ford Prefect, Zaphod Beeblebrox, Marvin the Paranoid Android, Trillian, and Slartibartfast—are separately described.
